        "text_BctwwL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Deep Hydration & Elasticity Support</strong><br/>Hyaluronic Acid (HA) and Elastin work in synergy to replenish moisture levels and restore skin suppleness, while grape sprout extract delivers antioxidant protection — helping reduce collagen breakdown and maintain a smooth, plump complexion.</p><p><strong>High-Performance Collagen Activation</strong><br/>84,000mg of deep-sea tuna collagen, combined with Vitamin C and camellia seed extract, actively stimulates natural collagen production up to 3–4 times more efficiently — improving skin firmness, resilience, and overall vitality from within.</p><p><strong>Skin Brightening & Pigmentation Control</strong><br/>Sakura extract targets tyrosinase activity to help reduce melanin formation, while Vitamins C and E provide powerful antioxidant defense — visibly improving uneven skin tone and enhancing natural radiance.</p><p><strong>Targeted Skin & Body Defense</strong><br/>Brazil nut and a complex of Vitamins A, D, and E help strengthen cellular integrity, boost glutathione production, and protect against oxidative stress — supporting concerns like acne, sensitivity, wrinkles, and pigmentation at the root.</p><p><br/>EVERY INGREDIENT HAS A PURPOSE. EVERY BOTTLE IS A COMPLETE SYSTEM — NOT JUST A COLLAGEN DRINK.</p><p></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
