          "settings": {
            "title": "Does 82X Koharu Collagen help with hydration?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. The formula includes <strong>Hyaluronic Acid (HA), Elastin, and grape sprout extract</strong>, which work together to deeply hydrate and support the skin. These ingredients help provide intense moisture, reduce dryness and rough texture, and keep the skin soft and smooth.</p><p>At the same time, they offer strong antioxidant benefits, help prevent premature aging, and protect collagen from breakdown — improving skin elasticity and leaving it looking firmer, plumper, and more radiant.</p>",
